<figureCitation id="A01D71F73CF20C024AC337F845AD5DAF" captionStart="Figures 11–19" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 11 - 19. Paraleptomenes transfoveolus sp. nov. Holotype (♀) 11, 13, 15, 16, 18, 19 paratype (♂) 12, 14, 17. 11, 12 habitus (dorsal view) 13, 14 head (frontal view) 15 mesosoma (dorsal view) 16 vertex and part of pronotum (dorsal view) 17 A 5 - A 13 18 tegula (dorsal view) 19 mesosoma (lateral view)." figureDoi="10.3897/jhr.90.82546.figures11-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/677828" pageId="0" pageNumber="185">19</figureCitation>
